extendedInfo.description: Buy. Sell. Shop. AutoSMART: the one-stop shop for all your car buying AND selling needs. Using our app you can quickly and easily sell your car online in 3 simple steps. Once your listing has been approved (usually takes one business day) it will be searchable on our nationwide network of over 1 million Credit Union members, both on our mobile apps, and the web.Not ready to post your car for sale yet? You can just look around and see how everything works. Search our database of vehicles for sale - not just from major car dealers, but from individuals just like yourself.Not sure you know what you want to buy? Take your time reading all of our research articles and find out what vehicle is best for you. You can also check us out on the web at www.cudlautosmart.com to build and configure the car of your dreams.And the best part? Buying a car from an authorized CUDL dealer means that you can get Credit Union financing right at the dealership! Not a Credit Union member? No problem! We even have tools that will help you find a local Credit Union that you are eligible to become a member of.Using our Loan Approval tools, you can quickly apply for a loan with your Credit Union. Just give us the basic data, and within 30 seconds you will know whether or not you have been approved, as well as the term and rate for your auto loan.Have you already been preapproved? You can search for the details and use your Credit Union financing right at the dealership!So whether youâre buying or selling, AutoSMART is the one place you can do it allâ¦ for FREE!

reviews.title: Has potential, misses the mark
reviews.comment: Three stars because the interface is great, ease of use is quite straight forward on initial use.  Only the stars because it is not up to date and irrelevant- I was looking for a Subaru Outback and it came up with one that had been sold two months prior and removed from the dealership internet site and didn\'t come up with two that were in the area.   Android 4G
